<html>
<head>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            background-color: #f3f3f3;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        h2, h3, h3 a, p {
            font-family: Helvetica Neue Light, Helvetica, Arial;
            color: #414141;
        }

        h3 {
            font-family: Helvetica Neue Bold, Helvetica, Arial;
            color: #FFF;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #e32552;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 300%;
        }

        #inner {
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
            width: 60%;
            height: 60%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="inner">
    <h2>${activity}</h2>

    <h3>F</h3>

    <p>Practice makes perfect, ${username}.</p>

    <p>You completed your trial of the <strong>${activity}</strong> task in <strong>${duration}</strong> seconds. You received a <strong>failing</strong>
        score because you made <strong>${error_number}</strong> errors.</p>

    <h3><a href="${video_url}">View Video</a></h3>

</div>
</body>
</html>
